g.text: Level 3 MDR Diagram for Listing/Search Operation Requests
Sends HTTP request to list the default operation requests
This part will behave the same way as the representation below
but without any filters being applied.
Sends HTTP request to list the operation requests with filters
This will return a queryable list of all operation requests.
This means that other queries can be chained
to this one in order to filter the requests.
Returns the queryable list of all operation requests
Returns the queryable list of requests filtered by Operation Type
Returns the queryable list of requests filtered by Deadline Date
Returns the queryable list of requests filtered by Priority
Returns the final list of operation requests
